public class BasicSapereAgent
extends SapereAgent

The implementation provided for Data LSA. Once a Data LSA is injected in the Space, it is no longer on control of the entity that injected it, i.e., the events that happens to the LSA are not reported

Author:
Gabriella Castelli (UNIMORE)
